(1489, 1, 'team', '{\"name\":\"Nguy\\u1ec5n Ti\\u1ebfn D\\u0169ng\",\"model\":\"Botble\\\\Team\\\\Models\\\\Team\",\"slug\":\"nguyen-tien-dung\",\"slug_id\":\"376\",\"is_slug_editable\":\"1\",\"description\":\"Th\\u1ef1c hi\\u1ec7n ki\\u1ec3m tra, b\\u1ea3o tr\\u00ec, l\\u1eafp \\u0111\\u1eb7t v\\u00e0 s\\u1eeda ch\\u1eefa h\\u1ec7 th\\u1ed1ng\\/s\\u1ea3n ph\\u1ea9m k\\u1ef9 thu\\u1eadt theo ph\\u00e2n c\\u00f4ng.\\r\\nH\\u1ed7 tr\\u1ee3 k\\u1ef9 thu\\u1eadt cho kh\\u00e1ch h\\u00e0ng, b\\u1ed9 ph\\u1eadn kinh doanh ho\\u1eb7c s\\u1ea3n xu\\u1ea5t khi c\\u1ea7n thi\\u1ebft.\",\"content\":\"<p>V\\u1edbi tinh th\\u1ea7n c\\u1ea7u ti\\u1ebfn v\\u00e0 chuy\\u00ean m\\u00f4n v\\u1eefng v\\u00e0ng, anh D\\u0169ng ch\\u1ecbu tr\\u00e1ch nhi\\u1ec7m gi\\u00e1m s\\u00e1t, b\\u1ea3o tr\\u00ec v\\u00e0 h\\u1ed7 tr\\u1ee3 k\\u1ef9 thu\\u1eadt cho c\\u00e1c h\\u1ec7 th\\u1ed1ng v\\u1eadn h\\u00e0nh c\\u1ee7a c\\u00f4ng ty. Anh lu\\u00f4n s\\u1eb5n s\\u00e0ng gi\\u1ea3i quy\\u1ebft c\\u00e1c v\\u1ea5n \\u0111\\u1ec1 k\\u1ef9 thu\\u1eadt m\\u1ed9t c\\u00e1ch nhanh ch\\u00f3ng, \\u0111\\u1ea3m b\\u1ea3o hi\\u1ec7u su\\u1ea5t v\\u00e0 \\u0111\\u1ed9 tin c\\u1eady cao cho s\\u1ea3n ph\\u1ea9m v\\u00e0 d\\u1ecbch v\\u1ee5 m\\u00e0 ch\\u00fang t\\u00f4i cung c\\u1ea5p.<\\/p>\",\"title\":\"Technical Staff\",\"phone\":\"01123259241\",\"email\":\"ntd2002238@gmail.com\",\"address\":\"T\\u00f2a C2 , D\'Capital , \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1eddng Tr\\u1ea7n Duy H\\u01b0ng , ph\\u01b0\\u1eddng Trung H\\u00f2a , qu\\u1eadn C\\u1ea7u Gi\\u1ea5y, H\\u00e0 N\\u1ed9i, Vi\\u1ec7t Nam\",\"website\":\"https:\\/\\/hisotechgroup.com\\/\",\"location\":\"VietNam\",\"socials\":{\"facebook\":\"https:\\/\\/www.facebook.com\\/dunglaanh23\",\"twitter\":\"https:\\/\\/twitter.com\\/\",\"instagram\":\"https:\\/\\/www.instagram.com\\/\"},\"submitter\":\"apply\",\"language\":\"vi\",\"status\":\"published\",\"photo\":\"123fe298ce5fb2ec5dd3bbbb5e8b1d1c-copy.jpg\"}', 'updated', 'Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleW